00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:45,500
Deployment läuft auf lokalen RTX-Systemen genauso wie auf AWS, Google Cloud und Azure.

70
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:52,387
Employees will be supercharged by teams of frontier, specialized and custom-built agents they deploy and manage.

